                    <span>Normally if it says Stanek on the cover I buy it without hesitation but like another reader I wondered if I should get the 2nd edition when I saw it. As someone who read and highly valued the 1st edition of this book I was skeptical that the service pack 2 would have such a large impact. However, after I skimmed this book and ended up purchasing it I am glad I did. Service pack 2 changes so many things and is such an extensive upgrade that the 2nd edition is really helpful. The 2nd edition is much more detailed and helpful. The sections on networking and security are also a big help. The new chapters are very helpful. The new networking and security features are radically different and make this book a great purchase. I believe this book has made me more productive and really improved my use of the OS.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">5 stars and then some!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
